<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="c01a6151-5ea9-44d1-9413-6b772479e2c9" >

    <h3>Additional resources</h3> 
<p>Rethink the way you deliver assessments and final exams. Think about what learning outcomes you are trying to assess and what kind of feedback you need to provide to students.</p>
    





