<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="f4c633a2-3b50-41ad-8e5f-ec774ed979de" >

    <p>Create a self-running slideshow using a microphone or webcam which you can then share to your class using Google Drive. Microsoft PowerPoint is available for free to all Ryerson faculty and staff through the <a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/ccs/services/software/microsoft/#MSOffice">Office 365 Education program.</a></p>
    
